# Text to List
import ast

# Import & Edit data automatically.
temp = open('/home/rakhan/PBH_data/lHTab.csv')
Data = [line.strip().strip('"') for line in temp]
for i, mass_group in enumerate(Data):
    Data[i] = ast.literal_eval(mass_group)

# Extract t, $\lambda$
for i in range(165,176):
    locals()['t_'+str(i)] = []
    locals()['lambda_'+str(i)] = []
for i, mass_group in enumerate(Data):
    for values in mass_group:
        locals()['t_'+str(i+165)].append(values[0])
        locals()['lambda_'+str(i+165)].append(values[2])

plt.show()

    if lambda3_55[i] < lambda3_55[i+1]:
        print('170.8555: t=' ,33+0.0001*i,' log10(t)=', log10(exp(33+0.0001*i)))
        break
for i in range(len(lambda3_56)-1):
    if lambda3_56[i] < lambda3_56[i+1]:
        print('170.8556: t=' ,33+0.0001*i,' log10(t)=',log10(exp(33+0.0001*i)))
        break
